               <head>Ta'rikh-i Muzaffari</head>
               <msContents>
                  <summary>1 copy of Tārīkh-i Muẓaffarī by Muḥammad ʿAlī Khān Anṣārī</summary>
                  <msItem class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2008115920" n="1" xml:id="Uk_IO_Islamic_3983-item1">
                     <author>
